### ============================================
### 3.1 GET ALL TASKS
### ============================================

### Get All Tasks (with Pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Tasks with Filter (pending)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Tasks with Filter (completed)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?status=completed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Tasks with Search
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?search=Parking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Tasks with Pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

